column1: #Text=DS : It has n't affected you then ?
#Text=DS : Every single person I interview I ask about the war because I think it 's important and it has affected me .
#Text=Then you must have a human spirit unmatched since Billy Graham made his first speech ! I mean you have to have a real conscience , social conscience , to care .
#Text=Where are the protests coming out of the Ivy League or the University of Alabama ?
#Text=They 're not there because there 's no conscription .
#Text=He 's the only voice in Congress that ever said that and he said it five years ago .
#Text=I do n't know of any other voice .
#Text=I am not aware of another member of the Congress who said what Rangel said .
#Text=Certainly not these candidates , Clinton and the rest of them .
#Text=Because they know it would stop the war in an hour .
#Text=The ridiculous stickers , â€˜ Support Your Troops ' on the back of an SUV ?
#Text=The cost of gas matters not at all .
#Text=DS : That 's the only thing that does seem to motivate people to be against the war is to be paying more at the gas pump .
#Text=Americans are unaffected , except those in the military or related to military people , does n't matter ...
#Text=I mean , yes you can have conversations at dinner parties about this , but it 's very political .
#Text=It 's about whether McCain says this or Hillary says this and what 's the position of somebody in the defense department .
#Text=DS : Does it bother you that there 's a lack of outrage ?
#Text=And it does bother me that the poor people who need money join the National Guard Reserves because they needed that money or they want to go to college .
#Text=What most bothers me are the college students â€“ the worst generation is what I call them .
#Text=These college students are the worst and I 've been to a lot of campuses .
#Text=I always go to USC in the spring in April every year .
#Text=I go for a week or so .
#Text=Across from the campus , there 's a motel I stay in .
#Text=College students are always hanging around there .
#Text=And I was , this year , at the University of Pennsylvania and I was at the University of Alabama , and I 've been to a number of campuses this year and nobody cares about this war .
